sub_title: Head of Merchant Operations - EMEA at Uber
summary:
I am eager to learn and grow every day because I want to accomplish results and create value for the world. 

I am an engineer by training, with an entrepreneurial heart. I am good at optimizing customer experience and operational efficiency.  I am passionate to build and grow the technology business.

I am currently leading EMEA Merchant Operations at Uber.
